                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Long ago, a merchant who lost his memory was wandering in the rainforest and wandered into the Withering by accident, and found himself surrounded by monsters. Thankfully, nearby Forest Rangers saved him in time. As of the present, the merchant has used this experience as a whetstone for his resolve, seeking to channel the intensity he witnessed in that moment to overcome all the challenges in his life...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
